attr.title: Foreign Frugglers
attr.desc: Eight brave survivors need to protect mother earth from spacey invaders in this pixelated arcade style 2d shoot 'em up. Use different types of weapons to shoot those bastards, rack up your score, and don't get 'Fruggled'.
attr.inst: Purchase the game from itch.io (https://ultimogames.itch.io/foreignfrugglers) or Steam (https://store.steampowered.com/app/1071920/_Foreign_Frugglers), download, and copy Foreign Frugglers.exe to foreignfrugglers/assets
attr.inst_md: Purchase the game from [itch.io](https://ultimogames.itch.io/foreignfrugglers) or [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/1071920/_Foreign_Frugglers), download, and copy `Foreign Frugglers.exe` to `foreignfrugglers/assets`
